name: TÅKEN v1
details:
Arrhythmic dual-head delay with random modulation and effect loopTåken is an asynchronous dual-head delay with random modulation and a powerful send/receive-loop. A tool for conjuring psychedelia and nostalgia sparingly or in excess. Tåkens arrhythmic functions offer a surprisingly musical way to break up a traditional delays linear, predictable behavior. The insert loop expands upon this by allowing integration and regeneration of external effect pedals. Experiment away!
